    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丛林在呼唤……你会回应吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/b3eb8da9d58d4e56e4f50f0bbfa0d281.poster.avif?t=1768719747\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/b3eb8da9d58d4e56e4f50f0bbfa0d281.webm?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/b3eb8da9d58d4e56e4f50f0bbfa0d281.mp4?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验流畅的冲刺式移动系统。扮演疯狂冲刺的猿猴，没有速度上限，释放你的野性！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多种动作和跑酷技巧：冲刺、滑行、跳扑、猛砸……或者搭配猿猴开发的香蕉炸弹技术组合使用。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他猿猴竞争，登上排行榜，成为最强灵长类！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/373e2ed780647eef1476777a7d9cd12f.poster.avif?t=1768719747\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/373e2ed780647eef1476777a7d9cd12f.webm?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/373e2ed780647eef1476777a7d9cd12f.mp4?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控由“粑粑动力”驱动的原始武器库，把快乐直接送进你的猴脑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在可破坏的环境中横冲直撞，击败提基邪教、赛博军团和上古生物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用黑市血清和稀有神器强化你的猿猴，打造专属猴子流派。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/04d51e828936932c6f20b1e95b3e0da4.poster.avif?t=1768719747\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/04d51e828936932c6f20b1e95b3e0da4.webm?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124360/extras/04d51e828936932c6f20b1e95b3e0da4.mp4?t=1768719747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上猿猴冒险之旅，探索茂密丛林、古老神庙、霓虹都市，还有隐藏的秘密领域。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与当地NPC成为朋友，在猿猴岛放松钓鱼，享受美味的猴子晚餐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >听多元风格的音乐，包括合成器浪潮、邦戈鼓点、摇滚等。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
